title: Fingerstyle Guitar Lesson: Finding Transition Points with Martin Taylor
fulltitle: Fingerstyle Guitar Lesson: Finding Transition Points with Martin Taylor
description:
In this fingerstyle guitar lesson, ArtistWorks guitar instructor Martin Taylor (http://artistworks.com/martin-taylor) breaks down the process of finding transition points in your playing. At the Online Fingerstyle Guitar School, you can get access to hundreds of prerecorded lessons, as well as exchange videos directly with Martin Taylor in a Video Exchange®.  Click the link for more free samples!~ 

Don't be intimidated if this is not at your level quite yet. Martin Taylor's Online Fingerstyle Guitar School provides lessons for all levels of playing. The greatest tool we offer is Video Exchange Learning. This revolutionary new method is a resource for you to learn directly from Martin Taylor. No limits. If you have a question on anything or just want some feedback on your playing  - just record a video and send it directly to Martin. He will do the same with a response. 

Lastly, all the other exchanges Martin Taylor and his students share will be posted on an ever growing library of exchanges on the school's website. There, you can access master class learning and learn from others people's playing from all around the world and benefit from the advice Martin gives everyone in the Video Exchanges®. 

Join today!

Find out more at http://artistworks.com/martin-taylor
